snippet.title: Undisputed Release Date Announcement Trailer (ESRB)
snippet.description:
We're excited to announce that Undisputed will be coming to PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S and PC Steam (1.0) on October 11, 2024. 

Get the Digital Deluxe WBC Edition and play early on October 8, 2024. Get the Physical Deluxe WBC Edition on PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S to receive the official WBC patch! Terms and conditions apply.

Are you ready to rule the ring and  #BecomeUndisputed 🥊?

Website: https://playundisputed.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayUndisputed
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/undisputed_sci/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PlayUndisputed/
TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@playundisputed

#Boxing #FightingGames #BoxingGame #VideoGames #Undisputed #RuleTheRing
